A divine weapon that can summon...
heroes? If that is truly how I was
brought here, then perhaps father...$k$pOh, don't mind me!

My father once served the royal
family of Faerghus. But he left,
abandoning the kingdom...

Wow! Don't you ever take a break?
Overworking yourself is nothing to
take lightly... Take it from me.

I've been studying, but there's this
passage I'm having trouble with...
Would you mind taking a look?

I borrowed a book from the castle
library... Books are expensive in
Fódlan, so I'm reading all I can!

Hi! I'm here to wish you all the best
from $Nf!
Ooh! That felt oddly good!
I hope I'm not letting anyone down...
I'm sorry... I'll do better, I promise!
Thank you! You won't regret this!

Hi! I'm Annette Fantine Dominic, and
I go to Garreg Mach Academy... Oh!
And you can call me "Annie"!

Sometimes I feel like nothing I try to
do ever works out. Do you ever feel
like that, $Nu?$k$pThe task ahead of you is so immense.
Summon Heroes! Save the world!
That sure is a lot of pressure...$k$pMy recommendation is...don't try to
do it all alone. It never ends well.
Trust me. I'm a bit of an expert.$k$pThat same urge made me anxious
when I first arrived here, but...look
at me now, thanks to your support!$k$pI just wanted to say, I'll do my best
for you as long as I'm here. You can
count on me returning your support!

Laundry, studies, training... I have my work cut out for me!

Need help with anything? No? Oh...

My dearest wish is for my family to reunite.
I know I should be taking it easy, but that's too hard!
I'll do my best for you, no matter how hard things get!
Yay!
